headline: Investment Firm Elliot Calls for Honeywell Restructuring in Letter to Board
summary: As Honeywell’s largest active investor, Elliott Investment Management’s letter to Honeywell International argued that Honeywell should split into two entities—Honeywell Aerospace and Honeywell Automation.
